title: WTF Happened to my Champions Page?
body:
It says Karthus but there's a pic of Lissandra?? I've never played lissandra on this account lol wat
http://i.imgur.com/4lZONBf.png
[](http://i.imgur.com/4lZONBf.png)

Refreshed page, won't go away.

replies.body: It looks like this is probably caused by corrupt files, so I'd give you client a quick restart just in case it immediately goes away. If it doesn't hit that cog icon in the top-right of your client, then hit the *Initiate Full Repair* button, then check this page again to see if it's been resolved.
